lead_paragraph: Australia coach Michael Cheika cut six players from his wider training squad on Friday, still leaving him with a bumper pool of 33 players from which to select his matchday 23 for next week's first test against England.

headline.print_headline: Hodge Retained as Cheika Pares Wallabies Squad
